rael-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-asked-sinwar-is-it-worth-10-000-gazans-dying-he-said-even-100-000-is-worth-it/0000018e-d40a-d5ed-adcf-f79af56c0000</guid></item><item><title>下班的以色列警察因道路纠纷杀死了 50 岁男子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/off-duty-israeli-officer-kills-50-year-old-man-following-dispute-on-the-road/0000018e-d379-d45f-abcf-f37d08fc0000</link><description>以色列警方称，周五，美国大使馆一名文职雇员在一场道路争吵中，据称拿出一把刀刺伤了一名休班官员的手。这名军官随后开枪打死了这名平民</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 18:38:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/off-duty-israeli-officer-kills-50-year-old-man-following-dispute-on-the-road/0000018e-d379-d45f-abcf-f37d08fc0000</guid></item><item><title>搜寻失踪 14 岁以色列人期间发生冲突，巴勒斯坦人死亡，三名以色列士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-3-israeli-soldiers-wounded-in-clashes-during-search-for-missing-boy/0000018e-d32e-d5ed-adcf-f3be28b00000</link><description>安全部队与巴勒斯坦人在 Al-Mughayyir 镇搜寻 14 岁的 Binyhamin Ahimeir 时爆发冲突，Binyhamin Ahimeir 在离开前哨站放牧牲畜后失踪</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-3-israeli-soldiers-wounded-in-clashes-during-search-for-missing-boy/0000018e-d32e-d5ed-adcf-f3be28b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 189 天：哈马斯哈尼亚称儿子被杀不会影响停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-189-hamas-haniyeh-says-sons-killing-wont-affect-truce-talks/0000018e-d316-d5ed-adcf-f396502c0000</link><description>法国、英国、加拿大、印度、波兰和澳大利亚向以色列、约旦河西岸、伊朗和黎巴嫩发出旅行警告 ■ 国防部长加兰特会见美国中央司令部负责人 ■ 欧盟对哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织的军事部门实施制裁 ■ 哈马斯政治领导人哈尼亚表示儿子被杀不会影响停战谈判 ■ 寻找失踪的 14 岁以色列人，约旦河西岸爆发冲突 ■ 战争结束 189 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-189-hamas-haniyeh-says-sons-killing-wont-affect-truce-talks/0000018e-d316-d5ed-adcf-f396502c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的鲁莽已成为内塔尼亚胡的政策选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-recklessness-has-become-netanyahus-policy-of-choice/0000018e-d243-df04-adae-ffd335120000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡多年来未能起草伊朗政策，现在他拒绝概述加沙战后战略。完全是为了迎合内部政治目标，才导致战争中的轻率轰炸</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:17:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-recklessness-has-become-netanyahus-policy-of-choice/0000018e-d243-df04-adae-ffd335120000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判中证人的苦难表明总理对以色列的腐败有多深</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/witness-ordeal-in-netanyahu-trial-shows-how-deeply-the-pm-has-corrupted-israel/0000018e-d149-df04-adae-fddb13780000</link><description>警察准将。敢于挑战内塔尼亚胡的科雷什·巴努尔将军为自己的职业生涯付出了代价——本周在法庭上，他遭到了法官的严厉质问和冷遇。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/witness-ordeal-in-netanyahu-trial-shows-how-deeply-the-pm-has-corrupted-israel/0000018e-d149-df04-adae-fddb13780000</guid></item><item><title>支持内塔尼亚胡的抗议者因“比比是杀人犯”的标语而殴打耶路撒冷居民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/pro-netanyahu-protesters-punch-jerusalem-resident-over-bibi-is-a-murderer-sign/0000018e-d17f-df04-adae-fdfff90a0000</link><description>在该男子阻止他们攻击他挂起标语的妻子后，示威者高喊种族主义口号。警方将双方分开并没有逮捕任何人</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:15:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/pro-netanyahu-protesters-punch-jerusalem-resident-over-bibi-is-a-murderer-sign/0000018e-d17f-df04-adae-fdfff90a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在约旦河西岸冲突中打死两名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-two-palestinians-in-west-bank-clashes/0000018e-d197-d01b-abdf-f9ff445f0000</link><description>以色列国防军证实已击毙穆罕默德·奥马尔·达拉格梅，据他们称，他指挥了恐怖活动。他的父亲是哈马斯成员，10 月 7 日后被捕，两周后在以色列拘留期间死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:47:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-two-palestinians-in-west-bank-clashes/0000018e-d197-d01b-abdf-f9ff445f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生部要求医院鼓励工作人员在加沙囚犯医疗机构工作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hospitals-asked-to-encourage-staff-to-work-at-medical-facility-for-gazan-prisoners/0000018e-d151-d97b-adcf-d57f22270000</link><description>医疗机构的工作人员担心违反法律，与以色列极端组织和被拘留者本人发生冲突，造成人员短缺，卫生部和医院院长正在努力解决这一问题，部分原因是为了减轻民用医院的治疗负担</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:39:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hospitals-asked-to-encourage-staff-to-work-at-medical-facility-for-gazan-prisoners/0000018e-d151-d97b-adcf-d57f22270000</guid></item><item><title>真主党落入黎巴嫩陷阱，时间在流逝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-is-in-lebanons-trap-and-the-clock-is-ticking/0000018e-d126-df04-adae-fdf6813f0000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉的亲密政治伙伴表示，黎巴嫩不会为以色列提供扩大战争的借口。该组织继续与伊朗保持单独的战线，同时忙于向该国南部的难民发放救济金</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-is-in-lebanons-trap-and-the-clock-is-ticking/0000018e-d126-df04-adae-fdf6813f0000</guid></item><item><title>两次暗杀，同样的问题：以色列没有考虑后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-didnt-consider-tehran-before-it-struck/0000018e-cea8-df04-adae-effa69000000</link><description>以色列国防军正在准备对大马士革伊朗大使馆大院遭到的袭击做出回应，似乎没有深入考虑杀害伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在加沙的家人可能造成的后果。美国的支持提供了安全感，但暴露了以色列威慑力的削弱</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 03:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-didnt-consider-tehran-before-it-struck/0000018e-cea8-df04-adae-effa69000000</guid></item><item><title>从拉法到耶路撒冷甚至美国：没有人再相信内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/from-rafah-to-jerusalem-and-even-the-u-s-no-one-believes-netanyahu-anymore/0000018e-ce5e-d283-a5ee-fedf821b0000</link><description>当首相宣布“有一个日期”时，他的意思是什么？ ■ 拜登区分了对以色列的支持和对内塔尼亚胡的支持 ■ 在返回人质的可怕证词和有关仍被囚禁者的悲观情报后，军方领导人改变了语气</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/from-rafah-to-jerusalem-and-even-the-u-s-no-one-believes-netanyahu-anymore/0000018e-ce5e-d283-a5ee-fedf821b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对伊朗警告加倍强调：“不要”；以色列国防军拦截两架真主党无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article-live/u-s-expects-iranian-attack-on-israel-as-gallant-vows-appropriate-response/0000018e-d003-d01b-abdf-f87fee120000</link><description>拜登警告伊朗：“不要” ■ 以色列国防军发言人表示，以色列已为各种伊朗袭击场景做好准备 ■ 多个国家因担心局势升级而向以色列发出旅行警告 ■ 在约旦河西岸寻找失踪男孩的冲突中，巴勒斯坦人丧生，三名以色列士兵受伤 ■美国和欧盟制裁哈马斯和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 02:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article-live/u-s-expects-iranian-attack-on-israel-as-gallant-vows-appropriate-response/0000018e-d003-d01b-abdf-f87fee120000</guid></item><item><title>“小时候，我住在日本的一个基布兹。他们接待我们作为志愿者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-12/ty-article/.highlight/as-a-boy-i-lived-on-a-kibbutz-in-japan-they-received-us-as-volunteers/0000018e-cf85-d5ed-adcf-ff976f220000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位渴望将人与自然联系起来的导游，以及一位在意大利获得身临其境体验的文学学生</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 00:08:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-12/ty-article/.highlight/as-a-boy-i-lived-on-a-kibbutz-in-japan-they-receive